{"tid":364041,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"雲南10天遊","createTime":"2017-08-18T05:24:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T19:59:17.000Z","uid":108915,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b8edbc7647bef144b269ef7a3d31878cac90650a","tid":364041,"uid":108915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T05:24:55.000Z","msg":"同女朋友半年多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁岩撞正佢生日就plan去佢想去好耐既雲南<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去個陣唔知醒 8點機我地6點幾先出門口<br />\n死趕爛趕好彩趕到<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/18/075311_37ed6e84e4037d0b577165aade3c74f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F18%2F075311_37ed6e84e4037d0b577165aade3c74f5.jpg&h=1bc2fe2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲夠時間買杯Starbucks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/18/075312_a90ebfbe0b038dc09fb9e06c25e05a8a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F18%2F075312_a90ebfbe0b038dc09fb9e06c25e05a8a.jpg&h=79ce59d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎緊應該係去到昆明轉火車<br />\n第二日去到麗江就坐大巴去香格里拉<br />\n不過仲未book住宿<br />\n有無去過既巴打知香格里拉有無咩地方平靚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住去納柏海同埋飛來寺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知啲交通 有無巴絲熟路可以話比me知 咁樣玩會唔會唔順路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6d6281b7a33e27a5700aad571bf298abd97f95","tid":364041,"uid":87608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T05:29:43.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ed51a394e7dff48a041f2f12a6884a30f7ba3e","tid":364041,"uid":22496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T11:18:36.000Z","msg":"香格里拉 去松贊林寺 普達措公園 <br />\n納柏海 如果唔騎馬就唔建議去"},{"pid":"3703479d4642b7587ae076d77fccce941364873a","tid":364041,"uid":29431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T11:20:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同女朋友半年多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁岩撞正佢生日就plan去佢想去好耐既雲南<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去個陣唔知醒 8點機我地6點幾先出門口<br />\n死趕爛趕好彩趕到<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/18/075311_37ed6e84e4037d0b577165aade3c74f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F18%2F075311_37ed6e84e4037d0b577165aade3c74f5.jpg&h=1bc2fe2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲夠時間買杯Starbucks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/18/075312_a90ebfbe0b038dc09fb9e06c25e05a8a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F18%2F075312_a90ebfbe0b038dc09fb9e06c25e05a8a.jpg&h=79ce59d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎緊應該係去到昆明轉火車<br />\n第二日去到麗江就坐大巴去香格里拉<br />\n不過仲未book住宿<br />\n有無去過既巴打知香格里拉有無咩地方平靚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住去納柏海同埋飛來寺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知啲交通 有無巴絲熟路可以話比me知 咁樣玩會唔會唔順路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n納帕海而加好似未有水,有水就好靚<br />\n如果未搵旅館建議住背包十年"},{"pid":"0c565cffd5e008b4ee2f5837443e42cc32ccb2d7","tid":364041,"uid":32390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T14:04:02.000Z","msg":"去雲南無得唔去瀘沽湖 真係好靚"},{"pid":"61935dd18bdec838f4917e143c4097044598f725","tid":364041,"uid":24147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T16:27:53.000Z","msg":"納柏海幾靚  不過留唔到耐<br />\n飛來寺其實幾細 同埋無乜野行 不過可以早起身睇日照金山 幾靚<br />\n不過去得飛來寺 唔怕辛苦應該去埋雨崩<br />\n雨崩真係值得一去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a7b2527089ccca681634d90147c7b5b2d1ea484","tid":364041,"uid":10345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T16:41:57.000Z","msg":"22號去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  去雨崩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   push下"},{"pid":"847c35b5d1febf1701868f5ecce5c89440bb7ca1","tid":364041,"uid":24147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T16:59:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>納柏海幾靚  不過留唔到耐<br />\n飛來寺其實幾細 同埋無乜野行 不過可以早起身睇日照金山 幾靚<br />\n不過去得飛來寺 唔怕辛苦應該去埋雨崩<br />\n雨崩真係值得一去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去到香格里拉可以住90主題青旅 或自由生活青旅<br />\n留一日香格里拉周圍行下 順便問下老闆第二日有無人一齊去飛來寺可以拼車 <br />\n第二日去飛來寺可以同師傅講順路睇埋納帕海 <br />\n去到飛來寺睇下有無興趣去雨崩 無就應該留一日就會想走 因為嗰度無乜野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見你直接去香格里拉 無時間適應 小心有高反<br />\n同埋回程有時間考慮去埋瀘沽湖同麗江古城"},{"pid":"02025d5028a8fbb0dbc7b8509105dd0e247c3394","tid":364041,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T18:28:12.000Z","msg":"得果10日..<br />\n咪麗江&gt;香格里&gt;大理咁玩囉<br />\n或麗江&gt;瀘沽湖&gt;香格里拉,,睇自己興趣啦<br />\n<br />\n或麗江&gt;香格里拉&gt;雨崩<br />\n<br />\n第3個較辛苦,行!"},{"pid":"b6d68ec13550975e32175b715dbad5818fffdb6c","tid":364041,"uid":106471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T19:45:11.000Z","msg":"瀘沽湖同雨崩係必去<br />\n<br />\n你得個十日時間，我建議你淨係去依兩個地方，真心真係好靚好靚"},{"pid":"18b07cf8fea4689cc1dcdc07e7901e898f22e1ec","tid":364041,"uid":106471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T19:48:18.000Z","msg":"去到麗江休息一晚，之後早上直沖瀘沽湖，記得要提早一晚買巴士票，係瀘沽湖玩3日2夜，之後出黎直上香格里拉，之後沖埋上飛來寺，係飛來寺休息一晚，之後就上雨崩3日2夜，之後原路返麗江走人，十日岩岩好"},{"pid":"4c391f104c735260b05a5e874cd50709201650c3","tid":364041,"uid":138366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T19:59:17.000Z","msg":"唔上雪山 可以skip麗江 極商業化 間間鋪賣嘅嘢都差唔多<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Between準備好十日瘋狂聽麗江小倩</span>"}]}